<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n40173a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40173a">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40173a"> 173(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ 3 breaths in / his face, baptism </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The seventh canon of the Council of Constantinople (381) advises that the baptism of certain kinds of heretics include an exorcism by three breaths expelled into their face and ears (cf. Augustine, Ep. 194.46).  <br>Raphael transcription: <a name="c10041g" href="c10all.htm#c10041g">VI.C.10:041(g)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
